id, \u201cWhat is Islam?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cKind words and feeding the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20441,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/07\/sabr-iman-yaqin\/","url_meta":{"origin":37394,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Conviction: Patience half of faith, certainty all of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"'Alqamah reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cPatience is half of faith and conviction is faith in its entirety.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 9083 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u00a0\u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064f \u0646\u0650\u0635\u0652\u0641\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0642\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064f \u0643\u064f\u0644\u0651\u064f\u0647\u064f 9083\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24282,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/patience-first-strike-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":37394,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sabr: Reward for patience at first strike is Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty says: O son of Adam, if you are patient and restrained at the first shock of calamity, I would not be pleased with any reward for you less than Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1597 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21842,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/04\/allah-sends-trials-benefit\/","url_meta":{"origin":37394,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Allah tests those He loves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Mahmud ibn Labid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf Allah loves a people, He afflicts them with trials. Whoever is patient is given patience, and whoever is anxious is given anxiety.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 23641 Grade: Jayyid (very good) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37394","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dail